<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 06 Jul 2024 12:12:06 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列国防军袭击真主党目标；以色列北部数十个社区响起火箭和无人机警报</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-06/ty-article-live/hamas-tells-hezbollah-it-agreed-to-proposed-cease-fire-in-gaza-netanyahu-says-gaps-remain/00000190-85b4-d0d9-a1f9-a7f624ec0000</link><description>巴勒斯坦报道称，六名巴勒斯坦人在西岸被以色列国防军炮火打伤 ■ 以色列国防军在加沙沙贾亚找到远程火箭发射器和恐怖隧道竖井 ■ 哈马斯告诉真主党，它同意拟议的停火协议，内塔尼亚胡称“仍然存在差距” ■ 真主党表示将采取行动一旦以色列和哈马斯之间开始停火，就停止战斗</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jul 2024 02:03:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-06/ty-article-live/hamas-tells-hezbollah-it-agreed-to-proposed-cease-fire-in-gaza-netanyahu-says-gaps-remain/00000190-85b4-d0d9-a1f9-a7f624ec0000</guid></item><item><title>镜头没有说谎，以色列军队有一种运送受伤巴勒斯坦人的新方式：在吉普车的引擎盖上</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-07-06/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/the-idf-has-a-new-way-of-transporting-wounded-palestinians-on-the-hoods-of-jeeps/00000190-8562-dd1f-adb9-ad6ff0ad0000</link><description>上周，不止一名，而是三名受伤、半裸的巴勒斯坦人遭到以色列国防军士兵的羞辱，他们强迫他们躺在滚烫的车辆上，并在杰宁周围游街示众。军方正在淡化这些事件</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jul 2024 01:50:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-07-06/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/the-idf-has-a-new-way-of-transporting-wounded-palestinians-on-the-hoods-of-jeeps/00000190-8562-dd1f-adb9-ad6ff0ad0000</guid></item><item><title>针对强大的以色列定居者团体的国际制裁可能会带来惊天动地的影响</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-06/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/mounting-international-sanctions-against-israeli-settler-group-could-be-earth-shattering/00000190-853d-dc2c-a9fa-e57d20fa0000</link><description>阿马纳组织与以色列所有银行以及居住在该组织家园的数千名定居者都有联系。加拿大实施的制裁延长可能会引发定居点运动的地震</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jul 2024 00:10:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-06/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/mounting-international-sanctions-against-israeli-settler-group-could-be-earth-shattering/00000190-853d-dc2c-a9fa-e57d20fa0000</guid></item><item><title>99 年，奥斯陆协议的制定者为以色列的未来描绘了严峻的愿景。事实证明它非常准确</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-06/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/in-99-ron-pundak-had-a-stark-vision-of-israels-future-it-was-painfully-accurate/00000190-8478-db02-a398-8d7901ad0000</link><description>《奥斯陆协议》的缔造者之一罗恩·庞达克 (Ron Pundak) 在 1999 年对以色列 2025 年的情况做出了噩梦般的预测。今天，在他去世十年后，这一切已经非常接近现实了</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 23:29:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-06/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/in-99-ron-pundak-had-a-stark-vision-of-israels-future-it-was-painfully-accurate/00000190-8478-db02-a398-8d7901ad0000</guid></item><item><title>甚至在哈马斯做出回应之前，内塔尼亚胡就试图破坏人质交易</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-06/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-tried-to-derail-the-hostage-deal-even-before-hamas-responded/00000190-7f58-df13-a798-ffd8b3ad0000</link><description>以色列总理渴望在任何协议中发挥作用，他的同谋贝扎雷尔·斯莫特里奇也有同样的态度。 -法西斯立法</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 21:01:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-06/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-tried-to-derail-the-hostage-deal-even-before-hamas-responded/00000190-7f58-df13-a798-ffd8b3ad0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯在加沙人质协议第一阶段放弃了持久停火的要求</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article/hamas-informs-hezbollah-it-agrees-to-gaza-cease-fire-deal-netanyahu-gaps-remain/00000190-849d-d161-abd0-cdbddaec0000</link><description>真主党周五还表示，一旦加沙地带休战生效，真主党将停止战斗。然而，以色列总理内塔尼亚胡办公室表示，双方之间“仍然存在分歧”</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 20:58:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article/hamas-informs-hezbollah-it-agrees-to-gaza-cease-fire-deal-netanyahu-gaps-remain/00000190-849d-d161-abd0-cdbddaec0000</guid></item><item><title>如何在不影响间谍的情况下处理情报警告：阿什拉夫·马尔万的教训</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/how-to-address-an-intelligence-warning-without-putting-the-spy-at-risk/00000190-83fe-dff5-a5d2-8ffe47540000</link><description>以色列如何能够在不暴露其身份的情况下对情报官员的严重警告做出回应？ 1973 年 10 月的经验教训可能在 50 年后仍然适用</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 19:54:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/how-to-address-an-intelligence-warning-without-putting-the-spy-at-risk/00000190-83fe-dff5-a5d2-8ffe47540000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事第 273 天：美国官员称哈马斯在停战谈判中做出重大转变</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-273-firefighting-teams-subdue-most-fires-in-north-israel/00000190-83ce-de6b-a9d0-c7cf057c0001</link><description>以色列摩萨德负责人启程前往卡塔尔继续停战谈判 ■ 美国高级官员称，哈马斯立场重大调整后，停战谈判取得“突破” ■ 真主党副领导人：扩大与以色列的战斗目前“不可行” ■ 消防队在黎巴嫩猛烈火箭弹袭击后，以色列北部的大部分大火得到扑灭 ■ 战争进入 273 天后，您需要了解以下信息</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 17:01:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-273-firefighting-teams-subdue-most-fires-in-north-israel/00000190-83ce-de6b-a9d0-c7cf057c0001</guid></item><item><title>以色列说服真主党停火的途径取决于与哈马斯达成加沙协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article/.premium/israels-path-to-convince-hezbollah-to-hold-its-fire-hinges-on-striking-a-gaza-deal/00000190-8200-d161-abd0-cba90d1c0000</link><description>暗杀真主党高级指挥官是以色列近乎自动化的战术反应，随后来自黎巴嫩的猛烈攻击让人对其效用产生怀疑。 ■ 激进犹太定居者的暴行，包括对安全部队的袭击，令人震惊</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 16:21:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article/.premium/israels-path-to-convince-hezbollah-to-hold-its-fire-hinges-on-striking-a-gaza-deal/00000190-8200-d161-abd0-cba90d1c0000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦人报告以色列在约旦河西岸杰宁的袭击中造成七人死亡；以色列国防军称其目标是武装分子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-forces-raid-west-banks-jenin-palestinian-medical-sources-report-seven-dead/00000190-82e9-dff5-a5d2-8fe926850000</link><description>以色列国防军表示，巴勒斯坦武装分子被无人机从空中击中，造成杰宁旅特工和一名 54 岁男子在观看屋顶突袭时被狙击手击中身亡。红新月会称另有两人受重伤</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 13:30:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-forces-raid-west-banks-jenin-palestinian-medical-sources-report-seven-dead/00000190-82e9-dff5-a5d2-8fe926850000</guid></item><item><title>全面重新占领加沙并不能保证以色列人的安全。只会煽风点火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article/.premium/the-reoccupation-of-gaza-will-not-bring-security-or-deterrence-back-to-israel/00000190-8210-db02-a398-8f1920d10000</link><description>10 月 7 日彻底粉碎了以色列以定居点换取安全的任何想法，并削弱了以色列对其对手的威慑力。无论如何，即使以色列成为加沙地带事实上的管理机构，加沙地带仍将是一个流血的冲突地区</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 11:12:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article/.premium/the-reoccupation-of-gaza-will-not-bring-security-or-deterrence-back-to-israel/00000190-8210-db02-a398-8f1920d10000</guid></item><item><title>警方：三名不属于国防军的以色列人涉嫌于 10 月 7 日谋杀一名巴勒斯坦人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article/.premium/police-3-israelis-suspected-of-murder-of-palestinian-who-entered-israel-on-oct-7/00000190-81d6-db02-a398-8ddf30a40000</link><description>此案已经调查数月，但法院的禁言令现已解除。这三人涉嫌从阵亡士兵身上夺取武器，并用它们杀死了一名在袭击期间进入以色列的加沙巴勒斯坦人，消息人士称该人持有武器</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 09:09:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article/.premium/police-3-israelis-suspected-of-murder-of-palestinian-who-entered-israel-on-oct-7/00000190-81d6-db02-a398-8ddf30a40000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡办公室表示，摩萨德主席从多哈返回后，加沙谈判仍存在“差距”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article-live/idf-soldier-killed-in-gaza-u-s-sees-key-breakthrough-in-hostage-talks-top-official-says/00000190-809b-db02-a398-8d9bb8c20000</link><description>一名男子在以色列北部城市基亚特什莫纳地区被火箭弹击中受轻伤 ■ 法新社：哈马斯官员表示，该组织预计以色列将在周六上午之前对停火“想法”作出回应 ■ 真主党副领导人称扩大与以色列的战斗“是不可能的” “目前这不是一个可行的选择” ■ 真主党领导人纳斯鲁拉会见哈马斯代表团，讨论加沙局势和停火谈判 ■ 巴勒斯坦卫生部表示，在与以色列国防军特种部队交火后，六名巴勒斯坦人在约旦河西岸杰宁丧生</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 02:05:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article-live/idf-soldier-killed-in-gaza-u-s-sees-key-breakthrough-in-hostage-talks-top-official-says/00000190-809b-db02-a398-8d9bb8c20000</guid></item><item><title>为了结束以色列和巴勒斯坦的斗争，两个心理现实必须协调一致</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/for-the-israeli-palestinian-struggle-to-end-two-psychological-realities-must-align/00000190-802d-ddc5-a5db-d2ad86600000</link><description>是时候将治疗原则应用于看似永无休止的以色列-巴勒斯坦斗争了吗？</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 00:37:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/for-the-israeli-palestinian-struggle-to-end-two-psychological-realities-must-align/00000190-802d-ddc5-a5db-d2ad86600000</guid></item><item><title>“以色列人要友善得多。在意大利，你可能死在街上，没人会在乎”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-07-05/ty-article/.highlight/people-are-nicer-in-israel-in-italy-you-could-die-in-the-street-and-no-one-would-care/00000190-7ff6-dff5-a5d2-7ff6170d0000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：一对以色列和意大利夫妇过着童话般的浪漫生活，还有一位日本侨民，她的孩子们教她变得更像以色列人</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 23:55:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-07-05/ty-article/.highlight/people-are-nicer-in-israel-in-italy-you-could-die-in-the-street-and-no-one-would-care/00000190-7ff6-dff5-a5d2-7ff6170d0000</guid></item><item><title>这位以色列人如何从主要的比比支持者变成主要的反政府抗议者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/how-this-israeli-went-from-major-bibi-supporter-to-leading-antigovernment-protester/00000190-7f42-dff5-a5d2-7f621a770000</link><description>米哈尔·多伊奇 (Michal Deutsch) 保持着因抗议以色列政府而被捕人数的全国纪录</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 22:54:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/how-this-israeli-went-from-major-bibi-supporter-to-leading-antigovernment-protester/00000190-7f42-dff5-a5d2-7f621a770000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡派摩萨德负责人就以色列与哈马斯停战进行谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-sends-mossad-chief-to-negotiate-israel-hamas-truce-amid/00000190-7f31-d7c8-a9fb-fff92ffe0000</link><description>尽管遭到一些内阁成员的强烈反对，但在摩萨德负责人戴维·巴尼亚的领导下，以色列将在商定的框架内寻求归还剩余人质。美国总统乔·拜登周四在与内塔尼亚胡的电话中对这一消息表示欢迎</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 21:16:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-sends-mossad-chief-to-negotiate-israel-hamas-truce-amid/00000190-7f31-d7c8-a9fb-fff92ffe0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长指责本-格维尔阻止将加沙人从有争议的拘留中心转移出来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-ag-accuses-ben-gvir-of-thwarting-transfer-of-gazans-from-sde-teiman/00000190-7f7c-da69-adf5-7f7f20090000</link><description>巴哈拉夫-米亚拉在给内塔尼亚胡的信中警告说，如果以色列继续将巴勒斯坦人关押在斯德泰曼，将会产生“深远的后果”，人权组织称那里的条件是不人道的</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 21:03:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-ag-accuses-ben-gvir-of-thwarting-transfer-of-gazans-from-sde-teiman/00000190-7f7c-da69-adf5-7f7f20090000</guid></item><item><title>以色列批准在约旦河西岸修建近 5,300 套新住宅；非政府组织呼吁数十年来最大规模的土地掠夺</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-approves-nearly-5-300-west-bank-homes-ngo-calls-out-largest-land-grab-in-decades/00000190-7f66-da1d-a19a-ff7e671e0000</link><description>这些计划包括扩大西岸深处的定居点，并将前哨基地合法化为定居点内的“社区”。以色列财政部长表示，这些措施旨在对抗某些欧盟国家承认巴勒斯坦国</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 20:28:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-approves-nearly-5-300-west-bank-homes-ngo-calls-out-largest-land-grab-in-decades/00000190-7f66-da1d-a19a-ff7e671e0000</guid></item><item><title>援助官员称，沙特阿拉伯对加沙的援助受到以色列拉法过境点关闭的威胁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/saudi-arabias-gaza-aid-threatened-by-israels-rafah-crossing-closure-aid-official-says/00000190-7f09-da69-adf5-7f4f025d0000</link><description>一名沙特官员表示，“由于封锁，数百辆卡车现在堆积在拉法”，他担心援助会因向有需要的加沙人提供援助而面临“巨大限制”</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 20:12:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/saudi-arabias-gaza-aid-threatened-by-israels-rafah-crossing-closure-aid-official-says/00000190-7f09-da69-adf5-7f4f025d0000</guid></item></channel></rss>